border-top-radius = adds border to a especific side
background-atatchment: fixed

background-img:url('...');
background-repeat:no-repeat;              other options background-repeat:repeatx; background-repeat:repeaty;
background-position:center top;                  other options background-position: 100px 0px; background-position:0px 100px; background-position: -100px; background-position:top/center/bottom
background-size:cover;


This entire block of code lines can be enshortened like this:
ex: 
background: url('') no-repeat top cover/center;


PADDING (clockwise!)

padding : top right bottom left;
or
padding: top/bottom left/right;

MARGIN (clockwise!)

margin : top right bottom left;
or
margin: top/bottom left/right'
